div(ng-cloak='')
  .row
    .col-md-4
      span.hipster.img-responsive.img-rounded
    .col-md-8
      h1(data-translate='home.title') Welcome, Java Hipster!
      p.lead(data-translate='home.subtitle') This is your homepage
      div(ng-switch='vm.isAuthenticated()')
        .alert.alert-success(ng-switch-when='true', data-translate='home.logged.message', translate-values="{username: '{{vm.account.login}}'}")
          | You are logged in as user "{{vm.account.login}}".
        .alert.alert-warning(ng-switch-when='false', data-translate='global.messages.info.authenticated', translate-compile='')
          | If you want to 
          a.alert-link(href='', ng-click='vm.login()') sign in
          | , you can try the default accounts:
          br
          | - Administrator (login="admin" and password="admin") 
          br
          | - User (login="user" and password="user").
        .alert.alert-warning(ng-switch-when='false', data-translate='global.messages.info.register', translate-compile='')
          | You don't have an account yet? 
          a.alert-link(ui-sref='register') Register a new account
      p(data-translate='home.question')
        | If you have any question on JHipster:
      ul
        li
          a(href='http://www.jhipster.tech/', target='_blank', rel='noopener', data-translate='home.link.homepage') JHipster homepage
        li
          a(href='http://stackoverflow.com/tags/jhipster/info', target='_blank', rel='noopener', data-translate='home.link.stackoverflow') JHipster on Stack Overflow
        li
          a(href='https://github.com/jhipster/generator-jhipster/issues?state=open', target='_blank', rel='noopener', data-translate='home.link.bugtracker') JHipster bug tracker
        li
          a(href='https://gitter.im/jhipster/generator-jhipster', target='_blank', rel='noopener', data-translate='home.link.chat') JHipster public chat room
        li
          a(href='https://twitter.com/java_hipster', target='_blank', rel='noopener', data-translate='home.link.follow') follow @java_hipster on Twitter
      p
        span(data-translate='home.like') If you like JHipster, don't forget to give us a star on 
        a(href='https://github.com/jhipster/generator-jhipster', target='_blank', rel='noopener', data-translate='home.github') GitHub
        | !
